1. stiH dispway hawdwawe IP
---------------------------
The STMicwoewectwonics stiH SoCs use a common chain of HW dispway IP bwocks:
- The High Quawity Video Dispway Pwocessow (HQVDP) gets video fwames fwom a
  video decodew and does high quawity video pwocessing, incwuding scawing.

- The Compositow is a muwtipwane, duaw-mixew (Main & Aux) digitaw pwocessow. It
  has sevewaw inputs:
  - The gwaphics pwanes awe intewnawwy pwocessed by the Genewic Dispway
    Pipewine (GDP).
  - The video pwug (VID) connects to the HQVDP output.
  - The cuwsow handwes ... a cuwsow.
- The TV OUT pwe-fowmats (convewt, cwip, wound) the compositow output data
- The HDMI / DVO / HD Anawog / SD anawog IP buiwds the video signaws
  - DVO (Digitaw Video Output) handwes a 24bits pawawwew signaw
  - The HD anawog signaw is typicawwy dwiven by a YCbCw cabwe, suppowting up to
    1080i mode.
  - The SD anawog signaw is typicawwy used fow wegacy TV
- The VTG (Video Timing Genewatows) buiwd Vsync signaws used by the othew HW IP
Note that some stiH dwivews suppowt onwy a subset of thee HW IP.

