2. DWM / HW mapping
-------------------
These IP awe mapped to the DWM objects as fowwowing:
- The CWTCs awe mapped to the Compositow Main and Aux Mixews
- The Fwamebuffews and pwanes awe mapped to the Compositow GDP (non video
  buffews) and to HQVDP+VID (video buffews)
- The Cuwsow is mapped to the Compositow Cuwsow
- The Encodews awe mapped to the TVOut
- The Bwidges/Connectows awe mapped to the HDMI / DVO / HD Anawog / SD anawog

FB & pwanes         Cuwsow      CWTC     Encodews    Bwidges/Connectows
